*This page is maintained by the LLM. It is updated on every ingest to reflect the current synthesis across all sources.*

## Current Wiki State

The wiki contains **15 sources**, **22 entities**, **13 concepts**, and **3 syntheses** — a total of 52 pages forming a knowledge graph centered on the Transformer architecture, large language models, the emerging AI Agent ecosystem, alternative sequence modeling paradigms, a practical AI-powered financial stock selection system, a personal backend developer resume with practical AI/blockchain project experience, a fork of Anthropic's Claude Code CLI with enhanced openness and multi-model support, a comprehensive guide to 14 quantitative trading strategies for the A-share market, a threading rebuild test, a notification and messaging system, a user profile system, a data model overview, an admin backend system, a real-time price monitoring and alert system, and a stock data service providing unified data source management with multi-level fallback and caching.

